missionEventData.data1: Red 1 head to the jump point.

The captain of the Bixby, an Imperial Corvette that recently defected to the Rebel Alliance, confirmed reports that the Empire is planning a major offensive in this sector of Rebel space. He believes that a large imperial fleet will begin its campaign in the Dellalt system. In your A-Wing, you will undertake a scouting patrol to look for this fleet. Scan all craft, do not engage the enemy.

missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: Interesting. We're not reading any ships.

Ignore them. Just keep your speed up and scan ships as they exit.
Detecting four Corvettes exiting Hyperspace. Scan them.
Another group of Corvettes is exiting.

Two Imperial Frigates have entered the area. Scan them and then prepare to jump home. The situation is starting to get hot.
An Imperial Star Destroyer has entered the area and is launching Ties. Time for you to get out of there!
